{"lineNumber":57685,"originalJapaneseLine":"程なくして、包帯やら何やらを手に、","translatedEnglishLine":"Before long, holding bandages and such,"},

{"lineNumber":57686,"originalJapaneseLine":"メアリーが戻ってきた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Mary returned."},

{"lineNumber":57687,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………まさか、手当でもしようってのか。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...You don't mean to treat me or something, do you?"},

{"lineNumber":57688,"originalJapaneseLine":"　俺ァ人類の敵だぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'm the enemy of humanity.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57689,"originalJapaneseLine":"「でも、なんか死にそうだし」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"But you kinda look like you're about to die.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57690,"originalJapaneseLine":"「死にゃしねぇよ。ほっときゃ治る」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I'm not dying. If left alone, I'll heal.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57691,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うるさいな。助けてもらう側が選り好みするな！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Shut up. The person being helped shouldn't be choosy!\" "},

{"lineNumber":57692,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"....................\" "},

{"lineNumber":57693,"originalJapaneseLine":"一理あるんだか無いんだか分からない物言いに、","translatedEnglishLine":"His words were hard to judge whether they made sense or not,"},

{"lineNumber":57694,"originalJapaneseLine":"レイはどう反応すればいいのか分からなくなった。","translatedEnglishLine":"and Ray didn't know how to react."},

{"lineNumber":57695,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……こんな時間にガキが出歩いてるんじゃねェ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Kids shouldn't be wandering around at this hour."},

{"lineNumber":57696,"originalJapaneseLine":"　さっさと親の所に帰れ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Go back to your parents quickly.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57697,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あー。いねーんだ。あたしンち」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, they're not here. At my place.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57698,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………ふん」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Hmph.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57699,"originalJapaneseLine":"小さく、鼻を鳴らす。","translatedEnglishLine":"He made a small snort."},

{"lineNumber":57700,"originalJapaneseLine":"別に、珍しい話でもないはずだった。","translatedEnglishLine":"This shouldn't have been an unusual story."},

{"lineNumber":57701,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちょっと前に、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Not long ago,"},

{"lineNumber":57702,"originalJapaneseLine":"　とーちゃん血を吐いて死んじまって。","translatedEnglishLine":"my dad coughed up blood and died."},

{"lineNumber":57703,"originalJapaneseLine":"　酒飲みすぎだってーの」","translatedEnglishLine":"He drank way too much.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57704,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お袋は」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"And your mom?\" "},

{"lineNumber":57705,"originalJapaneseLine":"（っ…………）","translatedEnglishLine":"(…...)"},

{"lineNumber":57706,"originalJapaneseLine":"問い返した事に、レイ自身だけが内心で驚いていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Ray himself was surprised at having asked back."},

{"lineNumber":57707,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あー。かーちゃんはもっと前に","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, my mom left with another man a long time ago."},

{"lineNumber":57708,"originalJapaneseLine":"　他のオトコと出てった」","translatedEnglishLine":"She ran off with another guy.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57709,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ひっでーかーちゃんでさー。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"She's a terrible mom."},

{"lineNumber":57710,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あたしの顔見る度に、怖ぇ目で睨むんだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"Every time she saw my face, she'd glare at me with scary eyes."},

{"lineNumber":57711,"originalJapaneseLine":"『その顔を見せるな、気持ち悪い』とかってさー」","translatedEnglishLine":"Like, 'Don't show that face, it's disgusting.'\" "},

{"lineNumber":57712,"originalJapaneseLine":"己の不幸を、からりと笑う。","translatedEnglishLine":"She laughed off her own misfortune cheerfully."},

{"lineNumber":57713,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……他人に関わる余裕なんざ、無さそうだがな。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Seems like she has no energy to care about others."},

{"lineNumber":57714,"originalJapaneseLine":"　何で助ける。ペットでも拾ったつもりか」","translatedEnglishLine":"Why help? Does she think she picked up a pet or something?\" "},

{"lineNumber":57715,"originalJapaneseLine":"「バッカだな。困ってるとか、死にかけてるとか。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You idiot. If you see someone in trouble or almost dying,"},

{"lineNumber":57716,"originalJapaneseLine":"　見かけちゃったら、捨てとけないだろ。","translatedEnglishLine":"you can't just leave them behind."},

{"lineNumber":57717,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あたしの気分が悪い」","translatedEnglishLine":"It makes me feel bad.\" "},

{"lineNumber":57718,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それに魔人だって、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Besides, even a demon"},{"lineNumber":57719,"originalJapaneseLine":"　自分の背中には手、届かないだろ」","translatedEnglishLine":"can't reach their own back, right?\" "},

{"lineNumber":57720,"originalJapaneseLine":"「………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"................\" "}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ハッ。……人間じゃねェからな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hah... Because I'm not human."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだった。魔人だったな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's right. You're a demon, after all."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちったぁビビれよ。甲斐がねェ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You could at least be a little scared. It's no use otherwise."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「怖がられたいのか？　変わってるな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Do you want to be feared? That's unusual."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………そーじゃねェよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...That's not it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どう言ったものか、調子が狂う。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, it throws off my rhythm.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レイが二の句を探している内に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While Ray was searching for a reply,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: メアリーは勝手に立ち上がった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mary got up on her own.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちょっと待ってろ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Wait a moment!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言い捨てて、メアリーは駆け出した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She said that and dashed off.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……なんか、いつも走ってんな、あいつ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...That one sure is always running..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 受け答えをしていると、なんとなく巻き込まれる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Answering her somehow pulls me in.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 本当に、奇妙なガキだった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She really was a strange kid.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「戻ってきたぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm back!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 程なくして、包帯やら何やらを手に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before long, holding bandages and such,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: メアリーが戻ってきた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mary returned.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………まさか、手当でもしようってのか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...You don't mean to treat me or something, do you?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺ァ人類の敵だぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm the enemy of humanity."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも、なんか死にそうだし」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But you kinda look like you're about to die."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「死にゃしねぇよ。ほっときゃ治る」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm not dying. If left alone, I'll heal."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うるさいな。助けてもらう側が選り好みするな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Shut up. The person being helped shouldn't be choosy!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一理あるんだか無いんだか分からない物言いに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: His words were hard to judge whether they made sense or not,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レイはどう反応すればいいのか分からなくなった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Ray didn't know how to react.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……こんな時間にガキが出歩いてるんじゃねェ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Kids shouldn't be wandering around at this hour.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さっさと親の所に帰れ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go back to your parents quickly."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あー。いねーんだ。あたしンち」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, they're not here. At my place."
"...Hmph."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 小さく、鼻を鳴らす。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He made a small snort.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 別に、珍しい話でもないはずだった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This shouldn't have been an unusual story.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちょっと前に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Not long ago,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とーちゃん血を吐いて死んじまって。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: my dad coughed up blood and died.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 酒飲みすぎだってーの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He drank way too much."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お袋は」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "And your mom?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 問い返した事に、レイ自身だけが内心で驚いていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ray himself was surprised at having asked back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あー。かーちゃんはもっと前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, my mom left with another man a long time ago.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 他のオトコと出てった」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She ran off with another guy."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひっでーかーちゃんでさー。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "She's a terrible mom.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしの顔見る度に、怖ぇ目で睨むんだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Every time she saw my face, she'd glare at me with scary eyes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 『その顔を見せるな、気持ち悪い』とかってさー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Like, 'Don't show that face, it's disgusting.'"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 己の不幸を、からりと笑う。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She laughed off her own misfortune cheerfully.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……他人に関わる余裕なんざ、無さそうだがな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Seems like she has no energy to care about others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何で助ける。ペットでも拾ったつもりか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why help? Does she think she picked up a pet or something?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「バッカだな。困ってるとか、死にかけてるとか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You idiot. If you see someone in trouble or almost dying,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 見かけちゃったら、捨てとけないだろ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you can't just leave them behind.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしの気分が悪い」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It makes me feel bad."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それに魔人だって、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Besides, even a demon

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自分の背中には手、届かないだろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: can't reach their own back, right?"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Like, 'Don't show that face, it's disgusting.'"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 己の不幸を、からりと笑う。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She laughed off her own misfortune cheerfully.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……他人に関わる余裕なんざ、無さそうだがな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Seems like she has no energy to care about others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何で助ける。ペットでも拾ったつもりか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why help? Does she think she picked up a pet or something?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「バッカだな。困ってるとか、死にかけてるとか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You idiot. If you see someone in trouble or almost dying,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 見かけちゃったら、捨てとけないだろ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you can't just leave them behind.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしの気分が悪い」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It makes me feel bad."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それに魔人だって、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Besides, even a demon

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自分の背中には手、届かないだろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: can't reach their own back, right?"
